    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per the MRL 2 assessment plan for a Class II device with Medium model influence. CFD predictions of NIH demonstrate mean relative error of 8.4% against experimental data, and all RH values are below 1.0 confirming non-inferiority to the predicate device. The model is accepted for the stated COU of identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions.",
